---
title: Grilled Provençal Tofu and Pepper Sandwiches with Zippy Lemon Aioli and Fresh Salad
description: Take a trip to the south of France with this grilled tofu sandwich. Paired with a fresh salad and zippy lemon aioli, let us take you away!

